 again.","To prepare jars, place <b>500 g<b> water in mixing bowl. Place jars and lids upside down in the centre of the Varoma and steam <b><strong>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/strong>.<b>  Leave to drain - do not dry or touch the inside surfaces. Alternatively, thoroughly wash jars and lids in hot, soapy water. Rinse by pouring over boiling water. Prepare for filling, if needed, by placing on a clean tea towel in a roasting tin and heat in the oven at 100˚C until required.","<strong>Raspberry jam<\/strong>: substitute strawberries with <b>500 g<b> raspberries. Reduce cooking time to <b>8-10 minutes<b> according to preferred consistency.","<strong>Mixed berries jam<\/strong>: use a total of <b>250 g<b> strawberries and <b>250 g<b> raspberries. Reduce cooking time to <b>25-30 minutes.<b>"],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","55m","1"]}